{"id": 2495, "genre": 1001, "title": "社恐如你，都经历过哪些“终于松口气”的轻松时刻？", "description": "在自己的想象的对话中经常妙语连珠，我只是从来不把它们翻译到现实生活中来。（题图来自：iStock ©️ macrovector）", "record_count": 3581, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180801121510bwIK7vC0GyjVYuNM.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-09-13T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 298496, "content": "面试。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 468703}, {"id": 298499, "content": "上班路上碰到领导，故意说自己没吃早餐要去买，愉快告别", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1421303}, {"id": 298500, "content": "终于不用尬聊了。呼～", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1397054}, {"id": 298501, "content": "尬聊结束", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1113818}, {"id": 298503, "content": "就是不好意思才硬聊的，反正我是，结果是更加尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1440522}, {"id": 300552, "content": "相亲结束的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1453161}, {"id": 298506, "content": "同学没有要跟我打招呼的样子，从旁边走过去了", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1112477}, {"id": 298508, "content": "假装没有听到快递按门铃的声音，还好他一会发短信说放门口了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 48523}, {"id": 298509, "content": "来敲门的推销员走了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1374652}, {"id": 298511, "content": "辞职", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636017}, {"id": 298770, "content": "本来晚上要和同事聚餐，因为领导有事而临时取消", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1441317}, {"id": 298515, "content": "一个人走出健身房终于要回去的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1355267}, {"id": 298771, "content": "每天下班走出公司...", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 25749}, {"id": 300563, "content": "下面我们抽一个人，介绍一下XX。\n\n抽到最后一个还没到我.松气～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 610289}, {"id": 298517, "content": "在外面逛街，迎面走来老板和他的家人。\n这时被朋友一把抓到一边拍照。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1230166}, {"id": 298773, "content": "赶完方案。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 175861}, {"id": 298518, "content": "聚会结束，和朋友的朋友顺路一起回家， 有一个人先下车的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378846}, {"id": 298774, "content": "想出一件神秘的事情。", "image": "img/option/option/20180914124406TSPq1aJDtfcWdlsX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 175861}, {"id": 299543, "content": "和一群人一起吃饭纠结到底该不该先去买单 突然有人站起来说要买单 大家aa给他打钱 完美", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1447336}, {"id": 298520, "content": "一张桌子吃饭，不知道说啥？？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1282528}, {"id": 299544, "content": "回家进电梯 门关的一瞬间庆幸后面的人没跟上来", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1447336}, {"id": 299289, "content": "和不熟的人一起走，然后终于到了目的地，可以分道扬镳了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1446132}, {"id": 330524, "content": "开完组会", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1599458}, {"id": 298788, "content": "他说没事的，我说算了吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1440022}, {"id": 298533, "content": "面试的时候吹牛逼，怕面试官问我不会回答的问题。\n最后安然无恙的走出面试大楼，噫吁嚱真险。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433019}, {"id": 299048, "content": "客人终于走了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1325496}, {"id": 304681, "content": "一个人的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1463434}, {"id": 302129, "content": "自己买各种东西和去吃饭和别人有交流的时候呗 结束当然松口气啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1220487}, {"id": 299059, "content": "面试改为笔试的时候松了口气", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1444642}, {"id": 298807, "content": "过年期间从亲戚家出来的一刹那", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1441465}, {"id": 298556, "content": "老板娘今天没问我老板昨晚的行踪", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693756}, {"id": 298559, "content": "bug解决的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1440625}, {"id": 298815, "content": "老师问我问题，突然接了一个电话，等回来的时候句话忘了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1402850}, {"id": 298565, "content": "准备自我介绍时被告知时间不够所以取消了", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1413570}, {"id": 299333, "content": "跟半熟不熟的领导一起乘电梯，刚好又遇到迟到😖", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1446399}, {"id": 298829, "content": "聚会散了以后，独自一个人在回家的路上", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1243653}, {"id": 299092, "content": "面试终于结束了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1436026}, {"id": 298581, "content": "辞职被各种打感情牌最终还是走出了公司", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108975}, {"id": 299093, "content": "....", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1445032}, {"id": 298592, "content": "拒绝别人的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1440647}, {"id": 298856, "content": "不熟的人或长辈和我聊天终于走了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1441880}, {"id": 303721, "content": "终于抢先关闭了电梯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1468891}, {"id": 298858, "content": "全中怎么办", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1423782}, {"id": 300394, "content": "朋友生日聚会，只认识一两个人，等到切完蛋糕那一刻，可以走了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1452423}, {"id": 303211, "content": "远在两个校区 朋友突然说不来找我玩了 如释重负", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1464116}, {"id": 298604, "content": "当两个人的电梯只剩我自己的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1440665}, {"id": 298608, "content": "从老师办公室走出来的那一刻。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 877762}, {"id": 298865, "content": "老师终于没叫我在讲台上讲题", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1394597}, {"id": 298867, "content": "终于上台演讲完了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1394550}, {"id": 298869, "content": "和一个不太熟但是认识的同学一起等、搭宿舍电梯的两个人时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1442007}]}